  "title": "Preschool Cleaner 幼儿园清洁工",
  "description": "<p>Are you a nurturing and dedicated individual who loves working with children and food? Our preschool is looking for a passionate <strong>Cleaner</strong> to join our team!</p>\n<p>In this dual role, you'll be essential in keeping our little ones happy and healthy. You'll assist our head cook in preparing nutritious meals and snacks, ensuring every dish meets our high standards for safety and quality. You'll also be responsible for maintaining a clean and hygienic environment in our kitchen and around the school, making sure our young learners have a safe space to eat, play, and grow.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Cleaning &amp; Hygiene:</strong> Maintain cleanliness and sanitation in the kitchen, classrooms, and other common areas.</li>\n  <li><strong>Teamwork:</strong> Work closely with the kitchen and teaching staff to ensure a smooth and positive experience for our students.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have a positive attitude, a strong work ethic, and a genuine love for children, we would love to hear from you.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>How to Apply:</strong></p>\n<p>Please submit your resume to [enquiry@noblelandarts-learning.com.sg] or call us at [9668 7563]. We can't wait to meet you!</p>",
